---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Zelys ERP - Tu negocio en piloto automático" description="Sistema ERP en la nube con facturación electrónica SRI, control de inventario en tiempo real, POS y analíticos avanzados.">
  <!-- HERO SECTION WITH ELECTRIC GLOW -->
  <section style="position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 7rem 2rem 5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
    <div class="glow-spot" style="top: -100px; left: calc(50% - 150px); width: 400px; height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.2) 0%, transparent 75%);"></div>
    
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; position: relative; z-index: 10;">
      <div class="glass" style="padding: 0.4rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 99px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        <span style="display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; background-color: var(--brand-blue); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--brand-blue);"></span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: var(--text-primary);">Facturación SRI Autorizada al Instante</span>
      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: 4rem; max-width: 900px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        Impulsa tu negocio con confianza usando <span class="gradient-text">Zelys ERP</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 650px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Gestiona inventarios, analiza ventas en tiempo real y automatiza tu contabilidad. Todo en una plataforma moderna, potente y con 0ms de latencia de carga.
      </p>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <a href="https://in.zelys.app/register" class="btn-primary" style="padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.95rem;">
          Comenzar Ahora Gratis
        </a>
        <a href="#features" class="glass" style="padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.95rem; border-color: var(--border-glass); color: var(--text-primary);">
          Ver Demostración
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- HIGH FIDELITY MOCKUP OF THE ERP DASHBOARD -->
      <div class="glass aura-glow" style="width: 100%; max-width: 1050px; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0.5rem; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);">
        <div style="background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); overflow: hidden; font-family: var(--font-sans); text-align: left; display: flex; height: 500px;">
          <!-- Mock Sidebar -->
          <aside style="width: 220px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border-glass); background-color: var(--bg-secondary); padding: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <div style="width: 24px; height: 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--brand-purple) 100%); border-radius: 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                <span style="color: white; font-weight: 900; font-size: 0.75rem;">Z</span>
              </div>
              <span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Zelys ERP</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <div style="background-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08); color: var(--text-primary); padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;">
                <span>📊 Dashboard</span>
              </div>
              <div style="padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><span>📦 Inventarios</span></div>
              <div style="padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><span>🧾 Facturación</span></div>
              <div style="padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><span>👥 Clientes</span></div>
              <div style="padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center;"><span>⚙️ Configuración</span></div>
            </div>
          </aside>
          <!-- Mock Content Area -->
          <main style="flex: 1; padding: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; overflow: hidden; background-color: var(--bg-primary);">
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.85rem;">
              <span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Panel Resumen</span>
              <span style="color: var(--brand-blue); background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08); padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;">Empresa Aistermcon</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Metrics Cards -->
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem;">
              <div class="glass" style="padding: 1rem; border-radius: 10px; background-color: var(--bg-secondary);">
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Ventas del Mes</span>
                <h4 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 0.25rem;">$12,450.80</h4>
                <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #22c55e;">+12.4% vs anterior</span>
              </div>
              <div class="glass" style="padding: 1rem; border-radius: 10px; background-color: var(--bg-secondary);">
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Facturas Emitidas (SRI)</span>
                <h4 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 0.25rem;">342</h4>
                <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #22c55e;">100% autorizadas</span>
              </div>
              <div class="glass" style="padding: 1rem; border-radius: 10px; background-color: var(--bg-secondary);">
                <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Productos en Alerta</span>
                <h4 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 0.25rem; color: var(--brand-blue);">3 Bodegas</h4>
                <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Stock seguro</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Graph / Chart Mockup -->
            <div class="glass" style="flex: 1; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem; background-color: var(--bg-secondary); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; min-height: 150px;">
              <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;">Flujo de Ventas Semanal</span>
              <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; justify-content: space-around;">
                <div style="width: 24px; height: 40%; background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--brand-purple), var(--brand-blue)); border-radius: 4px;"></div>
                <div style="width: 24px; height: 60%; background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--brand-purple), var(--brand-blue)); border-radius: 4px;"></div>
                <div style="width: 24px; height: 50%; background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--brand-purple), var(--brand-blue)); border-radius: 4px;"></div>
                <div style="width: 24px; height: 85%; background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--brand-purple), var(--brand-blue)); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);"></div>
                <div style="width: 24px; height: 70%; background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--brand-purple), var(--brand-blue)); border-radius: 4px;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </main>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES / PILARES SECTION -->
  <section id="features" style="background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass); padding: 7rem 2rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5rem;">
      <div style="text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; max-width: 600px;">Herramientas que transforman tu negocio</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 550px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Tres pilares fundamentales que impulsan el crecimiento de tu empresa con tecnología de vanguardia.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 2.5rem;">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="glass glass-interactive" style="padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--brand-blue); border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">📈</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">Analíticos Avanzados</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Dashboard inteligente con métricas en tiempo real. Visualiza el rendimiento de tu negocio con gráficos interactivos y reportes personalizados al instante.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="glass glass-interactive" style="padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--brand-purple); border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2);">📦</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">Gestión de Inventario</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Control completo de stock con alertas automáticas. Rastrea productos en múltiples bodegas, gestiona kardex y define conversiones de unidades UOM.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="glass glass-interactive" style="padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.08); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--brand-purple); border: 1px solid rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.2);">🛒</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">Ventas Inteligentes (POS)</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Procesa ventas al contado y a crédito de manera ágil. Genera facturas SRI, administra cuentas por cobrar y controla flujos de caja ciegos de forma centralizada.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TECHNOLOGY & ROBUSTNESS SECTION -->
  <section style="padding: 7rem 2rem; position: relative;">
    <div class="glow-spot" style="bottom: -50px; right: 10%; width: 350px; height: 350px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1) 0%, transparent 75%);"></div>
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4rem; position: relative; z-index: 10;">
      <div style="text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Tecnología que respalda tu negocio</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 600px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Integración nativa con entidades locales y almacenamiento en la nube altamente seguro y respaldado.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">🇪🇨</span>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">SRI Ecuador</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Autorización y firmas electrónicas integradas nativamente con el SRI.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">✉️</span>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Notificaciones Email</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Envío automatizado de comprobantes y recordatorios de cobranza por email.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">☁️</span>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Amazon S3</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Guardado seguro y privado de archivos, firmas y XMLs en AWS.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">💾</span>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Respaldos Diarios</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Copias automáticas en caliente para garantizar la cero pérdida de datos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING PLANS SECTION -->
  <section id="pricing" style="background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass); padding: 7rem 2rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4.5rem;">
      <div style="text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Planes simples adaptados a tu escala</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 550px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Precios transparentes y sin cargos ocultos. Comienza con una prueba gratuita de 14 días.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 2.5rem; justify-content: center;">
        <!-- Plan 1 -->
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Emprendedor</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem;">Ideal para pequeños comercios y profesionales independientes.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-primary);">$15</span>
            <span style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;"> / mes</span>
          </div>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            <li>✓ Hasta 100 facturas mensuales</li>
            <li>✓ 1 Bodega / Sucursal</li>
            <li>✓ Control de Inventario Básico</li>
            <li>✓ Soporte por Correo</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://in.zelys.app/register" class="glass" style="text-align: center; padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; border-color: var(--border-glass);">
            Elegir Emprendedor
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Plan 2 (RECOMENDADO) -->
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; border-color: var(--brand-blue); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);">
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Negocio / Pro</h3>
            <span style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); color: #60a5fa; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 99px;">RECOMENDADO</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: -1rem;">Para empresas en crecimiento y distribuidoras.</p>
          <div>
            <span style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-primary);">$35</span>
            <span style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;"> / mes</span>
          </div>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            <li>✓ Facturas mensuales ILIMITADAS</li>
            <li>✓ Múltiples Bodegas y Sucursales</li>
            <li>✓ Inventarios Avanzados y Kardex</li>
            <li>✓ Asistente de importación guiado</li>
            <li>✓ Soporte Prioritario 24/7</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://in.zelys.app/register" class="btn-primary" style="text-align: center; padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">
            Comenzar Prueba Gratis
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Plan 3 -->
        <div class="glass" style="padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Enterprise</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem;">Solución a la medida para grandes distribuidoras y cadenas.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-primary);">Personalizado</span>
          </div>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            <li>✓ Conexión directa vía API integrada</li>
            <li>✓ Integración dedicada con SRI</li>
            <li>✓ Servidor y base de datos exclusivos</li>
            <li>✓ Ejecutor de cuenta dedicado</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:soporte@zelys.app" class="glass" style="text-align: center; padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; border-color: var(--border-glass);">
            Contactar Soporte
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA / CENTRAL REGISTRY SECTION -->
  <section style="padding: 9rem 2rem; text-align: center; position: relative;">
    <div class="glow-spot" style="top: 20%; left: calc(50% - 175px); width: 350px; height: 350px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1) 0%, transparent 75%);"></div>
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; position: relative; z-index: 10;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.8rem; line-height: 1.15;">Toma el control de tus finanzas hoy</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 600px;">
        Únete a cientos de empresas locales que ya confían en Zelys ERP para facturar, gestionar stock y reportar al SRI sin demoras ni caídas.
      </p>
      <a href="https://in.zelys.app/register" class="btn-primary" style="padding: 1.1rem 3rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1.05rem;">
        Registrar mi Empresa Gratis
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
